    "body" : "<pre><code>DateTimeFormatter.ISO_INSTANT.format(Instant.now())\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>This saves you from having to convert to UTC.  However, some other language's time frameworks may not support the milliseconds so you should do </p>\n\n<pre><code>DateTimeFormatter.ISO_INSTANT.format(Instant.now().truncatedTo(ChronoUnit.SECONDS))\n</code></pre>\n"
