    "body" : "<p>I have same issue with @JsonFormat and lib 'jackson'.\nNeed set timezone:</p>\n<pre><code>@JsonFormat(pattern = &quot;yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss.SSSXXX&quot;, timezone = &quot;UTC&quot;)\n</code></pre>\n<p>In addition, to experiment with 'Instant' format you can write test:</p>\n<pre><code>@Test\nvoid pattern() {\n    Instant instant = Instant.now();\n\n    DateTimeFormatter dateTimeFormatter = DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern(&quot;yyyy MM dd&quot;)\n            .withZone(ZoneId.of(&quot;UTC&quot;));\n\n    String formattedDate = dateTimeFormatter.format(instant);\n    System.out.println(formattedDate);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Try change pattern &quot;yyyy MM dd&quot;, &quot;yyyy MMMM dd&quot;...</p>\n"
